./.title: Introduction

src/operations/.title: Operations
src/operations/.body:
Operations
There are several available operations:

set(object, path, value)
update(object, path, updater)
remove(object, path)

src/operations/set/.title: set(object, path, value)

src/operations/update/.title: update(object, path, updater)

src/operations/remove/.title: remove(object, path)

src/functional/.title: Functions
src/functional/.body:
Functions
Functions below can help to apply opertaions in functional way:

apply(value, ...ops)
pipe(value, ...ops)

src/functional/apply/.title: apply(value, ...ops)

src/functional/pipe/.title: pipe(value, ...ops)
